00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:41,774
Yes, abortion is legal.

531
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:44,818
When it was illegal

532
00:36:44,980 --> 00:36:48,132
in the years before the Revolution,

533
00:36:50,100 --> 00:36:55,698
